The habitats of the new species associated with existing nature trails in Knuckles mountains (
Bambaradeniya & Ekanayake 2003
). Dothalugala population located near a stream in existing Deanston–Dothalugala nature trail and Thangappuwa population located in wet, rocky surfaces along the existing Thangappuwa–Alugallena nature trail. Any situation in road clearing, weeding, constructions or maintaining, authorities should focus the attentions for management and further conservation attempts on this new species.
